author: Paul Smith
title: Aussie tech VC fund pulls the plug due to COVID-19 - The Australian Financial Review
description: Australia's technology start-up scene has suffered one of its first high profile victims of the coronavirus pandemic, with M8 Ventures saying it will close down.
